data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":225,"item_id":"msg_3d649b7155da65070069374850cf708190b896f221b84d3184","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso offers a product line under the brand \"Contoso Galaxy Innovations,\" specifically in the category of Smart Eyewear. This product is known for the following features:\n\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: Provides users with an interactive experience by overlaying digital information onto the real world.\n\n2. **Voice-controlled AI Agent**: Allows hands-free operation and interaction using voice commands, enhancing user convenience.\n\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Capable of recording high-definition videos accompanied by immersive 3-dimensional audio.\n\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Ensures eye safety by blocking harmful ultraviolet rays and reducing blue light exposure, which helps in preventing eye strain.\n\n5. **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: Comes with the facility for wireless charging and is designed to support long hours of usage without frequent recharging.\n\nAdditional information includes a two-year limited warranty on electronic components, and a 30-day return policy. For support, customers can contact at support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com.","logprobs":[]}

